{
  "stem": "1020.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Into a DP camp.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I, I was supposed to go to Munich, according-- what we read on the walls-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the dead telephones.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We found names that are cousins of ours out in Munich.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we planned to go to Munich.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "As we crossed the Czechoslovakian-German border, we were trying to walk and see if we can find any communication to have a ride wherever we want to go, to the nearest station to get a train or a bus.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we found a truck with wood-- a German.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we asked him where is he going?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He said, I'm going to Deggendorf.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't know Deggendorf.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't have any idea where Deggendorf was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But he told us that there's a railroad station in Deggendorf.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that's the way we planned to do to come into Munich, how to get there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So he took us on the truck on the road.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We're hungry.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And he drives.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It took him an hour or maybe less to come into Deggendorf.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was the Austrian-- if you look from that mountain from the station, Eisenstein-- Eisenstadt was the station there that-- we went through the border right on the station.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "From one side, you could see the Alps into Czechoslovakia, into Austria.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So the, the corner was Bavaria, Germany, Austria, and Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he says he's going to Deggendorf.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So, OK.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we're taking a ride, and we're coming in Deggendorf.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he stopped in the middle of the center town, across from city hall.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he-- this is here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We're getting off.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we're standing, like, looking around.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We're, we're from here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we're here.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "By-passers going down.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "People passing, they talk Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we stopped them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The name was Kelman.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I remember now the name.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we, we ask him in Yiddish, [YIDDISH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He says, yeah, [SPEAKING YIDDISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, our, our slogan after the war, to find out if anybody's a Jew-- we couldn't go over to a Polack, saying, you a Jew?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we said, [YIDDISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So a Jew knew what [YIDDISH] is.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[YIDDISH] is a Jew, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they says, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So they say, where are you going?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He says, from where are you?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I said, I'm from Poland.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "From where?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "From Bedzin.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Where are you going?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "To Munich.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Why do you have to go to Munich?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "That-- we have in here a DP camp, Displaced Persons.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we have in here a man from Bedzin.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He is on the committee.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And then another man which, by coincidence, was a brother-in-law to my brother-in-law, to my sister's husband-- a brother-in-law.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So we went, and we walked into that camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And that-- my sister's brother-in-law brought me a, a dish of butter, two pounds of butter, with the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But you took sick after that-- eating them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I was so hungry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it looked like we were trying to settle in that DP camp, 1945.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we settled in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And a matter of fact, I have a paper from that camp-- 45 years.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "As long as we-- the first Yiddish Hanukkah after the war, in that camp, we were celebrating.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we met already.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had one gathering from the DP camp in San Diego about six year, seven years ago-- from that DP camp from Deggendorf.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now we're going to meet in here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Probably tomorrow night or Saturday night, we'll have a dinner together, not too many people.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we'll find out tomorrow.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were going to get together.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Then we settled in DP camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There's-- my wife had two brothers in Canada, not knowing an address, but knowing a name-- an aunt, mother's sister-- sister of her mother by the name Rose-- two brothers Holender.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, when I came home--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When I came home to Bedzin-- we had also a committee in Bedzin when I came home for furlough before I was yet discharged.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And everybody went to that committee and also put the names down.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So if anybody decided to leave Bedzin like I left, we left our names behind.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If anybody will come later, or anybody came before us, which-- I couldn't locate [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] nobody from my family.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Which-- actually, before the war broke out, we didn't live in Bedzin.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We lived in another city, six kilometers, which the city was Dabrowa.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mentioned that to you, Dabrowa.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I gave you another address.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I think, now, [NON-ENGLISH] 33, in Dabrowa.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I didn't go to Dabrowa.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I don't know for what reason, but it was very scary.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Dabrowa didn't have many Jews before the war-- not as Bedzin.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was a Jewish city.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
